{"word":"Ω","slug":"Ω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Ω, ὦ</el></b> the last letter of the Greek alphabet <b>o(mega).</b> In <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> as symbol, in conjunction <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄλφα\">ἄλφα</a></el>, of an entity that controls everything from beginning to end: <el>τὸ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ω\">Ω</a></el> <b><a href='B:730 1:11'>Rv 1:11</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>;</b> <el>τὸ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὦ\">ὦ</a></el> <b><a href='B:730 1:8'>Rv 1:8</a>; <a href='B:730 21:6'>21:6</a>; <a href='B:730 22:13'>22:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ψώχω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὦ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}